<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-66-0955 </DOCNO><TEXT>We present an overview of the development of laser optics utilizing liquidcrystals. Devices discussed include wave plates, circular polarizers,optical isolators, laser blocking notch filters and laser beam apodizers.Issues addressesed include fabrication methods and laser damage resistance.</TEXT></DOC>